    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079100/extras/2a8e2e81edd7c9da3d09fdd317588bf8.poster.avif?t=1747753132\" width=640 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079100/extras/2a8e2e81edd7c9da3d09fdd317588bf8.webm?t=1747753132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079100/extras/2a8e2e81edd7c9da3d09fdd317588bf8.mp4?t=1747753132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Island Architect</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sculpt seaside towns nestled between cliffs in <i>Island Architect</i>, a relaxing free-form builder. Shape winding streets, carve tunnels, and craft cozy harbors in a world inspired by Mediterranean and Baltic architecture. No rules, no pressure—just pure creation.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shape Your World with Flowing Forms</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break away from regular grids — craft whimsical towers, cliff-side cottages, and winding alleyways with organic, flowing shapes. Dig sea caves, sculpt arches, and let the terrain shape your town naturally.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relaxing Coastal Charm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether a quiet fishing village or a grand seaside city, build at your own pace and embrace the tranquility.</p>",
